    • Content

      /**

probit of dropout probability based on obj and subj prob

@author Markus Schaffner
@date 21/12/2012

*/


clear all
set more off

cd "/Users/mas/Dropbox/EXPERIMENTS/OET/material"

log using "log/table2_prob_dropout.smcl", replace smcl

use "dta/oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta"

sort subjectid pitstopid

// list subjectid raceid pitstopid dropout

// create a proper dropout dummy, 0 = not yet droped out, 1 = drop out, . = prev drop out
gen dropoutD = .
replace dropoutD = 0 if pitstopnum == 1 & dropout == "false"
replace dropoutD = 1 if pitstopnum == 1 & dropout == "true"
replace dropoutD = 0 if pitstopnum == 2 & dropout == "false" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"
replace dropoutD = 1 if pitstopnum == 2 & dropout == "true" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"
replace dropoutD = 0 if pitstopnum == 3 & dropout == "false" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"
replace dropoutD = 1 if pitstopnum == 3 & dropout == "true" & dropout[_n-1] == "false"


gen pse = psexpectation / 1000
gen female = 0
replace female = 1 if gender == 1
gen age2 = age*age

gen ps2 = 0
replace ps2 = 1 if pitstopnum == 2

gen ps3 = 0
replace ps3 = 1 if pitstopnum == 3

// list subjectid raceid pitstopid pitstopnum dropout dropoutD

gen wbobj = 0
replace wbobj = 1 if winpc*winfactor < 0.40 & pitstopnum == 1
replace wbobj = 1 if winpc*winfactor < 0.25 & pitstopnum == 2
replace wbobj = 1 if winpc*winfactor < 0.10 & pitstopnum == 3

gen wbsubj = 0
replace wbsubj = 1 if pse*winfactor < 0.40 & pitstopnum == 1
replace wbsubj = 1 if pse*winfactor < 0.25 & pitstopnum == 2
replace wbsubj = 1 if pse*winfactor < 0.10 & pitstopnum == 3


// clean up relevant var names for the table
label var winpc "Objective prob."
label var pse "Subjective prob."

label var wbobj "Obj. cutoff"
label var wbsubj "Subj. cutoff"

label var female "Gender (female=1)"
label var age "Age"
label var age2 "Age$^2$"

label var ps2 "2nd pitstop"
label var ps3 "3rd pitstop"

local evalat = 0.10/winfactor 

probit dropoutD winpc if ps3 == 1 & slostakes == 0, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at( `evalat' )
estimates store e1a

probit dropoutD pse if ps3 == 1 & slostakes == 0, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at( `evalat' )
estimates store e1c

probit dropoutD wbobj  if ps3 == 1 & slostakes == 0, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at( `evalat' )
estimates store e1b

probit dropoutD wbsubj if ps3 == 1 & slostakes == 0, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at( `evalat' )
estimates store e1d

probit dropoutD wbobj wbsubj if ps3 == 1 & slostakes == 0, cluster(subjectid)
estimates store bothd


probit dropoutD winpc pse if ps3 == 1  & slostakes == 0, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at( `evalat'  `evalat' )
estimates store a3rd

probit dropoutD winpc pse, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at( `evalat'  `evalat' )
estimates store a1st


/*
probit dropoutD winpc wbsubj if ps3 == 1, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at(0.15 1)
estimates store e2c

probit dropoutD wbobj pse  if ps3 == 1, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at(1 0.15 )
estimates store e2d

probit dropoutD wbobj wbsubj if ps3 == 1, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at(1 1)
estimates store e2e

probit dropoutD pse wbsubj if ps3 == 1, cluster(subjectid)
mfx, at(0.15 1)
